description: Every exciting event in Sacramento simply isn’t complete without Dave and his scrumptiously authentic New Jersey Dawgs. This family-run fleet of trucks is serving up a tasty selection of premium specialty hot dogs and sausages, including Hebrew National 100% Kosher Beef Hot Dogs, Evergood Hot Links, Daily Chef Mozzarella & Roasted Garlic Chicken Sausage, and Lightlife Smart Dogs Veggie Hot Dogs, to name a few. These delicious handheld meals are perfect for every kind of party, picnic, festival, you name it. No matter what kind of shindig you're planning, just be sure to call on Dave's Dawgs...“No job is too big or too small – Dave’s Dawgs does it all!”
name: Dave's Dawgs
